data.description: A large beautifully designed 4-bedroom 3 bath all brick Lennar built home located in the classy Stewart Heights section of the Master Planned Community, Lakes of Savannah. Attention to every detail was considered in the design of this home. Lots of windows, Quartz countertops, custom white kitchen cabinets and crown molding throughout. The custom 8’ entry door leads into a grand foyer w/12' high ceilings. Your office has glassed framed French doors is located on your left, with a formal dining that opens to the kitchen on your right. Continue into your wide open and roomy living area which opens to the kitchen and breakfast room from the other side. At bedtime, settle into your spacious primary suite that boast a large bathroom with a jetted tub, separate glass enclosed shower, dual vanities, oversize closet and more! Out back, relax under the protection of your covered patio with enough yard for recreation. The pictures tell the story of a truly special home, in a wonderful community.
